                <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
              </svg>
              +56 9 3330 1114
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="mailto:contacto@exportandes.cl" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-accent-teal transition-colors duration-200">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="shrink-0"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="M22 7l-10 6L2 7"/></svg>
              contacto@exportandes.cl
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="shrink-0 mt-0.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg>
            Lunes a Viernes: 08:30 — 18:00
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Partners -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-sm font-heading font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Global Partners</h4>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <a href="https://aluwe.nl" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-3 group/partner">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-600 group-hover/partner:bg-white/10 group-hover/partner:text-gray-400 transition-all duration-200">
              <span class="text-xs font-heading font-bold">AW</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-400 group-hover/partner:text-gray-300 transition-colors">Aluwe</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-gray-600">aluwe.nl</div>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href="https://ingotsan.com" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-3 group/partner">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-600 group-hover/partner:bg-white/10 group-hover/partner:text-gray-400 transition-all duration-200">
              <span class="text-xs font-heading font-bold">IG</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-400 group-hover/partner:text-gray-300 transition-colors">Ingotsan</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-gray-600">ingotsan.com</div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-gray-700 mt-4">
          En alianza estratégica con empresas líderes en el reciclaje y fundición de metales a nivel global.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom Bar -->
    <div class="border-t border-white/5 py-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">
        &copy; {currentYear} Exportandes. Todos los derechos reservados.
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <span class="text-xs text-gray-700">Concepción, Chile</span>
        <span class="text-gray-800">·</span>
        <span class="text-xs text-gray-700">Región del Bio Bio</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
